name: Controlling Crows
description:
Today i wake up
The crows are gone
Only ashes remain
Why are they so different ?
I wander among the black shadows
Trying to catch a glimpse of their faces
But nothing appears, I'm falling
Please don't leave me, don't reject me
The world has ended, but I remain
Entwined in your arms I resist
To the maelstrom of the abyss
So that in the end the darkness collapses
And everything finally lights up
